      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.Item.2JEgdbpI3C3mfgHn]{Grim Determination (Combat)}</p>\n<p>In your most dire moments, you summon a primal desire to survive that pushes you beyond your limits.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Con 17</p><hr /><p>Once per day, when you spend Resolve Points to stay in the fight, you regain Hit Points equal to 1 + your Constitution modifier ([[/ max(0, floor(@abilities.con.mod + 1))]]), and you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to skill checks, attack rolls, and saving throws for a number of rounds equal to the Hit Points regained in this way.</p>"
